1
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:47,868
[suspenseful music playing]

2
00:00:52,268 --> 00:00:53,334
[Jerrod] Kitana...

3
00:00:53,467 --> 00:00:55,067
I have something for you.

4
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,400
It will protect you.

5
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,667
It's beautiful, Father.

6
00:01:02,467 --> 00:01:04,368
This was a gift
from Lord Raiden.

7
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,901
The God of Thunder.

8
00:01:07,001 --> 00:01:09,433
If anything
were to happen to me,

9
00:01:09,567 --> 00:01:11,634
he's always listening.

10
00:01:18,667 --> 00:01:21,467
[guard] Shao Kahn
is arriving, Your Majesty.

11
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:24,500
What happens if you lose?

12
00:01:24,634 --> 00:01:25,800
[Jerrod] Don't worry
about that.

13
00:01:25,934 --> 00:01:27,700
But what if he's too strong?

14
00:01:27,835 --> 00:01:30,301
Strength is not a closed fist.

15
00:01:30,433 --> 00:01:31,734
Strength is here,

16
00:01:32,868 --> 00:01:33,967
and here.

17
00:01:37,101 --> 00:01:39,167
Be strong, Kitana.

18
00:01:39,301 --> 00:01:40,901
[Jerrod sighs]

19
00:01:45,467 --> 00:01:50,400
[citizens chanting]
Jerrod, our king!
Jerrod, our king!

20
00:01:50,533 --> 00:01:52,868
[chanting continues]

21
00:02:04,934 --> 00:02:07,901
[Kitana] <i>Shao Kahn,</i>
<i>Emperor of Outworld,</i>

22
00:02:08,034 --> 00:02:11,835
<i>sought to unite the various</i>
<i>realms under one rule.</i>

23
00:02:11,967 --> 00:02:14,067
<i>His.</i>

24
00:02:14,201 --> 00:02:17,868
<i>But the Elder Gods had put</i>
<i>certain precautions in place.</i>

25
00:02:20,301 --> 00:02:23,835
<i>Our fates would not be settled</i>
<i>by the size of our armies.</i>

26
00:02:25,901 --> 00:02:29,567
<i>They would be decided</i>
<i>by combat.</i>

27
00:02:30,734 --> 00:02:32,835
<i>The rules were simple.</i>

28
00:02:32,967 --> 00:02:36,134
<i>If one realm could win</i>
<i>10 tournaments in a row,</i>

29
00:02:36,268 --> 00:02:39,368
<i>it would be given</i>
<i>dominion over the other.</i>

30
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:43,467
<i>Outworld would be allowed</i>
<i>to pillage Edenia's resources.</i>

31
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,567
<i>Enslave our people.</i>

32
00:02:50,268 --> 00:02:54,901
<i>This was the final tournament.</i>
<i>Our last chance.</i>

33
00:02:55,034 --> 00:02:58,101
<i>All of our greatest warriors</i>
<i>had already fallen.</i>

34
00:02:59,634 --> 00:03:01,901
<i>Only one fighter remained.</i>

35
00:03:02,034 --> 00:03:03,533
<i>My father,</i>

36
00:03:04,735 --> 00:03:08,001
<i>King Jerrod of Edenia.</i>

37
00:03:08,134 --> 00:03:11,433
<i>But he faced Outworld's</i>
<i>greatest warrior.</i>

38
00:03:13,467 --> 00:03:15,901
<i>Shao Kahn himself.</i>

39
00:03:18,201 --> 00:03:19,433
[gasps softly]

40
00:03:21,334 --> 00:03:23,801
[footsteps thudding]

41
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,801
[growls]

42
00:03:25,934 --> 00:03:30,167
They will never bow to you.

43
00:03:30,301 --> 00:03:32,234
[Shao Kahn] We shall see.

44
00:03:32,368 --> 00:03:34,533
[gong tolls]

45
00:03:35,701 --> 00:03:37,768
[tense music playing]

46
00:03:42,067 --> 00:03:43,134
[growls]

47
00:03:45,201 --> 00:03:46,634
[weapons clanging]

48
00:03:49,101 --> 00:03:50,868
-[Jerrod straining]
-[grunting]

49
00:03:53,634 --> 00:03:55,634
-[Jerrod yells]
-[thuds]

50
00:04:00,801 --> 00:04:02,268
[growls]

51
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,400
-[thuds]
-[citizens exclaim]

52
00:04:13,034 --> 00:04:14,533
[Jerrod yells]

53
00:04:16,067 --> 00:04:17,801
[gasps]

54
00:04:17,934 --> 00:04:19,134
[groaning]

55
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:29,635
Never!

56
00:04:39,034 --> 00:04:40,567
[weapon clatters]

57
00:04:40,701 --> 00:04:42,167
[blade slicing]

58
00:04:42,301 --> 00:04:43,735
[young Kitana gasps]

59
00:04:46,467 --> 00:04:49,034
-[grunts loudly]
-[Shao Kahn screams]

60
00:04:51,067 --> 00:04:53,101
-[blade slices]
-[Shao Kahn groans]

61
00:04:59,101 --> 00:05:01,635
[Jerrod strains, screams]

62
00:05:01,768 --> 00:05:03,500
[citizens gasping]

63
00:05:05,334 --> 00:05:06,934
[screams]

64
00:05:10,167 --> 00:05:12,433
[ominous music playing]

65
00:05:18,201 --> 00:05:20,034
[Jerrod grunting]

66
00:05:22,067 --> 00:05:23,934
[screaming]

67
00:05:25,034 --> 00:05:27,334
[gasps] Kitana,
close your eyes.

68
00:05:27,467 --> 00:05:28,934
Close your eyes right now.

69
00:05:29,067 --> 00:05:30,868
[pained groans]

70
00:05:32,835 --> 00:05:34,801
[breathing heavily]

71
00:05:38,668 --> 00:05:40,433
[yells in pain]

72
00:05:43,201 --> 00:05:46,301
-[screams]
-No!

73
00:05:46,433 --> 00:05:47,934
No!

74
00:05:48,067 --> 00:05:50,167
[struggling]

75
00:05:50,301 --> 00:05:53,500
No! [sobbing]

76
00:05:54,234 --> 00:05:56,433
[screaming]

77
00:05:58,835 --> 00:06:01,400
[somber music playing]

78
00:06:01,533 --> 00:06:02,868
[thuds]

79
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,067
[breath trembling]

80
00:06:09,835 --> 00:06:11,701
[crying]

81
00:06:16,101 --> 00:06:18,134
[women crying]

82
00:06:22,201 --> 00:06:23,901
[growls]

83
00:06:24,034 --> 00:06:27,334
[Shao Kahn] Edenia
now belongs to me.

84
00:06:27,467 --> 00:06:29,568
[sinister music playing]

85
00:06:48,368 --> 00:06:49,534
[dagger clanks]

86
00:06:49,668 --> 00:06:51,868
-[grunting]
-[blade clanging]

87
00:06:53,201 --> 00:06:54,400
[Sindel growls]

88
00:07:03,534 --> 00:07:05,467
[Sindel grunts]

89
00:07:05,601 --> 00:07:08,701
[Shao Kahn] Kneel.
Or you'll die.

90
00:07:26,835 --> 00:07:29,635
[mournful music playing]

91
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:09,868
[foreboding music playing]

92
00:08:15,934 --> 00:08:18,668
Your father shouldn't have
brought you here.

93
00:08:30,134 --> 00:08:33,134
Kitana,
you're my daughter now.

94
00:08:41,001 --> 00:08:44,434
[dramatic choral music playing]

95
00:08:47,401 --> 00:08:48,401
[woman] Kitana!

96
00:08:48,534 --> 00:08:50,101
[thrilling music playing]

97
00:08:51,034 --> 00:08:52,768
[both grunting]

98
00:08:55,001 --> 00:08:56,568
[panting]

99
00:08:58,134 --> 00:08:59,934
[weapons clacking]

100
00:09:03,001 --> 00:09:04,134
[Kitana grunts]

101
00:09:22,134 --> 00:09:23,835
[thrilling music stops]

102
00:09:25,268 --> 00:09:26,134
Yield.

103
00:09:43,201 --> 00:09:44,635
[ribbon snaps]

104
00:09:45,768 --> 00:09:47,934
You cannot be serious.

105
00:09:48,067 --> 00:09:50,901
You're the one who taught me,
everything's a weapon.

106
00:09:52,868 --> 00:09:55,101
[thrilling music resumes]

107
00:09:57,635 --> 00:09:59,268
[woman grunts]

108
00:09:59,401 --> 00:10:00,768
You yield.

109
00:10:15,134 --> 00:10:16,534
What do you have there?

110
00:10:16,668 --> 00:10:18,167
It's nothing.

111
00:10:19,568 --> 00:10:20,668
Jade.

112
00:10:22,701 --> 00:10:24,134
It was 20 years ago today

113
00:10:24,268 --> 00:10:26,601
the Emperor named me
as your bodyguard.

114
00:10:27,668 --> 00:10:29,967
I know what Shao Kahn
took from you.

115
00:10:30,101 --> 00:10:32,201
And if you had been vicious
or cruel to me,

116
00:10:32,335 --> 00:10:33,501
no one would have blamed you,

117
00:10:33,635 --> 00:10:36,501
but you treated me
like family.

118
00:10:37,468 --> 00:10:38,668
Like a sister.

119
00:10:40,635 --> 00:10:42,801
You are my sister.

120
00:10:42,934 --> 00:10:44,901
In every way that matters.

121
00:10:47,735 --> 00:10:51,701
Um, I got you something.
For the tournament.

122
00:10:56,468 --> 00:10:57,901
I was told
that a proper princess

123
00:10:58,034 --> 00:11:01,167
is supposed to sit around
on pillows fanning herself.

124
00:11:02,501 --> 00:11:03,835
Then I thought

125
00:11:03,967 --> 00:11:07,167
you are not exactly
the pillow type.

126
00:11:07,302 --> 00:11:08,967
[clanking]

127
00:11:11,635 --> 00:11:13,034
These are amazing.

128
00:11:16,302 --> 00:11:19,034
[suspenseful music playing]

129
00:11:26,201 --> 00:11:28,302
Hello, Mother.

130
00:11:28,434 --> 00:11:31,934
[Shao Kahn] I was beginning
to think you were avoiding me.

131
00:11:32,067 --> 00:11:34,868
I've been busy.
Training for the tournament.

132
00:11:36,501 --> 00:11:38,468
[Shao Kahn] Good.
Because I have petitioned

133
00:11:38,601 --> 00:11:41,067
the Elder Gods
for the tournament to begin.

134
00:11:41,202 --> 00:11:44,369
Let Raiden scrounge
for his little champions.

135
00:11:44,501 --> 00:11:47,134
They will simply
be the first to die

136
00:11:47,269 --> 00:11:49,134
and Earthrealm will be mine.

137
00:11:49,269 --> 00:11:50,934
-[gasps]
-[door opens]

138
00:11:55,601 --> 00:11:56,901
[Kitana] Why is he here?

139
00:11:57,034 --> 00:11:59,601
[Shao Kahn] I have a task
for Shang Tsung.

140
00:12:00,668 --> 00:12:03,401
I hope you bring
good news, Sorcerer.

141
00:12:03,534 --> 00:12:06,235
My spies have located
the relic.

142
00:12:06,369 --> 00:12:08,067
It was last seen
in Raiden's temple

143
00:12:08,202 --> 00:12:11,701
where it was stolen
by the mercenary, Kano.

144
00:12:11,835 --> 00:12:14,235
[Shao Kahn]
We seek the Amulet of Shinnok.

145
00:12:14,369 --> 00:12:17,302
[Sindel] It is said the Amulet
can heal any wound.

146
00:12:17,434 --> 00:12:19,534
Transform a man into a god.

147
00:12:19,668 --> 00:12:21,235
To charge the amulet
would require

148
00:12:21,369 --> 00:12:23,401
an impossible amount of power.

149
00:12:23,534 --> 00:12:26,468
We would need to capture
a star from the heavens.

150
00:12:26,601 --> 00:12:29,235
-A star...
-[dramatic music playing]

151
00:12:29,369 --> 00:12:31,768
...or a god.

152
00:12:31,901 --> 00:12:33,901
[Raiden] Outworld has issued
their challenge

153
00:12:34,034 --> 00:12:35,701
and the Elder Gods
have spoken.

154
00:12:35,835 --> 00:12:40,269
When the sand is gone,
the first round will begin.

155
00:12:40,401 --> 00:12:42,967
Mortal Kombat is upon us

156
00:12:43,101 --> 00:12:46,635
and yet we are still short
one champion.

157
00:12:48,067 --> 00:12:49,668
[static]

158
00:12:58,034 --> 00:13:01,568
-[tires screeching]
-[suspenseful music playing]

159
00:13:05,369 --> 00:13:06,768
["Rock You Like A Hurricane"
by Scorpions playing]

160
00:13:06,901 --> 00:13:09,302
[singer]
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

161
00:13:09,434 --> 00:13:14,868
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

162
00:13:40,668 --> 00:13:43,568
It's showtime.

163
00:13:43,701 --> 00:13:45,067
[man screams]

164
00:13:45,202 --> 00:13:48,135
["Rock You Like A Hurricane"
continues playing]

165
00:13:48,269 --> 00:13:50,434
♪ <i>Are you ready, baby?</i> ♪

166
00:13:59,501 --> 00:14:00,801
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

167
00:14:00,934 --> 00:14:01,967
[grunts]

168
00:14:02,102 --> 00:14:05,468
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

169
00:14:06,269 --> 00:14:07,335
[steel rod thudding]

170
00:14:07,468 --> 00:14:09,701
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

171
00:14:09,835 --> 00:14:11,967
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

172
00:14:12,102 --> 00:14:13,135
[growls]

173
00:14:17,601 --> 00:14:20,068
[singer vocalizing]

174
00:14:22,102 --> 00:14:24,468
[Johnny] You should have
brought more guys.

175
00:14:24,601 --> 00:14:26,102
♪ <i>The sun comes out</i> ♪

176
00:14:26,235 --> 00:14:30,135
♪ <i>Last night was shaking</i>
<i>And pretty loud</i> ♪

177
00:14:31,102 --> 00:14:31,901
[Johnny grunts]

178
00:14:32,035 --> 00:14:33,901
♪ <i>It scratches my skin</i> ♪

179
00:14:34,035 --> 00:14:38,035
♪ <i>So what is wrong</i>
<i>With another sin?</i> ♪

180
00:14:44,001 --> 00:14:46,102
♪ <i>Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah</i> ♪

181
00:14:46,235 --> 00:14:48,501
♪ <i>Here I am</i> ♪

182
00:14:48,635 --> 00:14:51,269
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

183
00:14:51,401 --> 00:14:53,901
♪ <i>Come on, come on</i>
<i>Come on, come on</i> ♪

184
00:14:54,035 --> 00:14:56,035
[explosion]

185
00:14:56,168 --> 00:14:57,668
♪ <i>Rock you like a hurricane</i> ♪

186
00:14:57,801 --> 00:14:59,735
[man 1] Man, Johnny Cage
got old as fuck.

187
00:14:59,868 --> 00:15:03,102
-[snoring]
-[girls shrieking]

188
00:15:05,701 --> 00:15:07,369
[announcer over speakers]
<i>Attention, fans,</i>

189
00:15:07,501 --> 00:15:09,501
<i>don't miss your chance to meet</i>
<i>your favorite influencers</i>

190
00:15:09,635 --> 00:15:12,434
<i>and YouTube stars</i>
<i>in Autograph Alley.</i>

191
00:15:12,568 --> 00:15:14,302
[woman] All right,
everyone, get in close.

192
00:15:14,434 --> 00:15:15,401
Black Orchid!

193
00:15:15,534 --> 00:15:17,967
[girls cheering]

194
00:15:18,102 --> 00:15:20,534
[upbeat dance music
playing over speakers]

195
00:15:25,369 --> 00:15:26,701
[Johnny] <i>It's showtime.</i>

196
00:15:42,501 --> 00:15:44,235
Johnny Cage.

197
00:15:44,369 --> 00:15:47,102
Hey, guys. I'm off the clock.

198
00:15:47,235 --> 00:15:51,302
Mr. Cage, you have been chosen
for Mortal Kombat.

199
00:15:51,468 --> 00:15:53,035
Mortal Kombat, huh?

200
00:15:53,168 --> 00:15:55,135
What's that?
Some kind of fan film?

201
00:15:55,269 --> 00:15:56,701
It's a fighting tournament.

202
00:15:56,835 --> 00:15:59,835
[sighs] Yeah, not really
my thing anymore.

203
00:16:01,701 --> 00:16:03,202
Unless it's a paying gig?

204
00:16:03,335 --> 00:16:06,002
More like a "fate
of the entire human race" gig.

205
00:16:06,135 --> 00:16:09,002
Tell me you're
not some crazy fans.

206
00:16:09,135 --> 00:16:10,701
Definitely not fans.

207
00:16:10,835 --> 00:16:12,701
All right. All right.
You don't
have to say "definitely."

208
00:16:12,835 --> 00:16:14,068
You have been chosen

209
00:16:14,202 --> 00:16:16,002
as one of the champions
of Earthrealm.

210
00:16:16,135 --> 00:16:19,601
The gods have selected you,
Mr. Cage.

211
00:16:19,735 --> 00:16:22,068
All right, I think it's time
for you guys to fuck off.

212
00:16:22,202 --> 00:16:24,635
But, hey, love the cosplay.
What's that?

213
00:16:24,768 --> 00:16:26,668
<i>Big Trouble in Little China?</i>
Fantastic film.

214
00:16:26,801 --> 00:16:28,369
Listen, I know
what it sounds like,

215
00:16:28,501 --> 00:16:29,868
but he's telling the truth.

216
00:16:30,002 --> 00:16:33,202
Very soon the champions
will be summoned to fight

217
00:16:33,335 --> 00:16:34,601
and you will be among them.

218
00:16:34,735 --> 00:16:36,035
The fate of your world

219
00:16:36,168 --> 00:16:38,668
rests on the outcome
of this tournament.

220
00:16:38,801 --> 00:16:41,335
Fantastic.
I will see you there.

221
00:16:41,468 --> 00:16:42,935
Thanks for coming, drive safe,

222
00:16:43,068 --> 00:16:45,335
and, uh, say hi to Dumbledore
for me.

223
00:16:45,468 --> 00:16:47,468
You're gonna have to show him.

224
00:16:51,168 --> 00:16:52,601
[crackling]

225
00:17:01,635 --> 00:17:04,035
Holy shit.

226
00:17:04,168 --> 00:17:05,468
How are you doing that?

227
00:17:05,601 --> 00:17:07,102
[Raiden] Come with us,
Mr. Cage,

228
00:17:07,235 --> 00:17:10,168
and discover the man
you were meant to be.

229
00:17:16,635 --> 00:17:18,434
Now are you coming or what?

230
00:17:23,701 --> 00:17:26,102
[mysterious music playing]

231
00:17:43,735 --> 00:17:46,534
Where the hell am I?

232
00:17:46,668 --> 00:17:48,568
[Sonya] It's okay.
You're still on Earth.

233
00:17:48,701 --> 00:17:50,434
Welcome
to Raiden's Sky Temple.

234
00:17:50,568 --> 00:17:52,902
[intriguing music playing]

235
00:17:53,035 --> 00:17:54,735
[all grunting]

236
00:17:56,935 --> 00:17:59,869
[Jax] Watch this. [grunts]

237
00:18:00,002 --> 00:18:04,035
Robot arms.
That dude's got robot arms.

238
00:18:04,168 --> 00:18:05,635
[Sonya] We served
in the Army together.

239
00:18:05,768 --> 00:18:08,068
That's Jax Briggs.
Special Forces.

240
00:18:09,302 --> 00:18:10,635
That's Cole Young.

241
00:18:10,768 --> 00:18:13,668
His suit absorbs attacks
and makes him stronger.

242
00:18:13,801 --> 00:18:15,135
He's a descendant of Scorpion.

243
00:18:15,269 --> 00:18:17,668
One of Earthrealm's
greatest warriors.

244
00:18:18,534 --> 00:18:19,468
Oh.

245
00:18:19,601 --> 00:18:21,434
That's Liu Kang.

246
00:18:21,568 --> 00:18:23,468
He's the best fighter we got.

247
00:18:31,968 --> 00:18:34,135
-He shoots fire?
-[Sonya] Mm-hmm.

248
00:18:34,269 --> 00:18:35,869
[scoffs]

249
00:18:36,002 --> 00:18:39,369
I feel like that's cheating,
but okay.

250
00:18:39,501 --> 00:18:40,668
It kind of feels like bullshit

251
00:18:40,802 --> 00:18:42,501
that y'all have
these crazy powers

252
00:18:42,635 --> 00:18:45,802
and I'm just, you know,
incredibly handsome.

253
00:18:45,935 --> 00:18:47,335
It could take
months of training

254
00:18:47,468 --> 00:18:49,002
to unlock your powers.

255
00:18:49,135 --> 00:18:50,468
We don't have
that kind of time.

256
00:18:50,601 --> 00:18:51,836
Yeah,
well, whose fault is that?

257
00:18:51,968 --> 00:18:53,568
I mean,
if you knew this was coming,

258
00:18:53,701 --> 00:18:55,035
why'd you wait till the
last second to find me?

259
00:18:55,168 --> 00:18:57,769
We used to have
another champion. Kung Lao.

260
00:18:57,902 --> 00:18:59,501
Oh, great,
so I'm just the fucking sub.

261
00:18:59,635 --> 00:19:01,635
He was murdered.
By Shang Tsung.

262
00:19:01,769 --> 00:19:04,102
Wait. Murdered?

263
00:19:05,701 --> 00:19:08,068
Come on.
You can't be serious. Right?

264
00:19:08,202 --> 00:19:10,968
I mean, that's, like,
gotta be against the rules.

265
00:19:11,102 --> 00:19:13,501
You can't just go around
killing people.

266
00:19:14,701 --> 00:19:18,035
It's called Mortal Kombat
for a reason.

267
00:19:18,168 --> 00:19:21,369
Yo, Gandalf, send me back.
I wanna go back.

268
00:19:21,501 --> 00:19:23,836
-Johnny, wait.
-No. No.

269
00:19:23,968 --> 00:19:25,769
You said tournament
which implies rules,

270
00:19:25,902 --> 00:19:27,836
and a referee, and I don't
know, maybe a medic.

271
00:19:27,968 --> 00:19:30,002
Not some fucking <i>Squid Game</i>
murder party.

272
00:19:30,135 --> 00:19:32,269
Dude wants to quit,
just let him go.

273
00:19:32,401 --> 00:19:33,736
We don't need him.

274
00:19:33,869 --> 00:19:36,501
Look, you wanna step
in the octagon

275
00:19:36,635 --> 00:19:38,002
with a bunch
of happy assholes

276
00:19:38,135 --> 00:19:41,235
that don't know how to lose,
go right ahead.

277
00:19:41,369 --> 00:19:43,568
But I don't have
Transformer arms,

278
00:19:43,701 --> 00:19:46,601
or shoot lightning bolts
or fireballs,

279
00:19:46,736 --> 00:19:49,068
or do whatever the fuck it is
Flame Fingers does,

280
00:19:49,202 --> 00:19:52,534
so forgive me if I don't
sign up to get mulched.

281
00:19:55,902 --> 00:19:58,468
You are not wrong, Mr. Cage.

282
00:20:06,434 --> 00:20:08,168
Nine times,
we have been challenged.

283
00:20:08,302 --> 00:20:10,068
And nine times, we have lost.

284
00:20:10,202 --> 00:20:11,769
And now, 20 years later,

285
00:20:11,902 --> 00:20:15,869
Shao Kahn seeks to add
Earthrealm to his dominion.

286
00:20:16,002 --> 00:20:19,869
This is a war
for the fate of your world.

287
00:20:20,002 --> 00:20:22,902
[Jax] Look, Cage, I get it.
We all do.

288
00:20:23,035 --> 00:20:24,836
Some stupid, fucking,
cosmic lottery

289
00:20:24,968 --> 00:20:28,135
decided that we're the ones
that get to save the world.

290
00:20:30,501 --> 00:20:32,369
Shit is terrifying.

291
00:20:32,501 --> 00:20:34,601
[Cole] You wanna know
the last thing I did
before coming here?

292
00:20:34,736 --> 00:20:38,002
I said goodbye to my wife
and my little girl.

293
00:20:38,135 --> 00:20:41,434
The two most important things
in my life.

294
00:20:41,568 --> 00:20:42,635
And there's a damn good chance

295
00:20:42,769 --> 00:20:44,836
I'm never
gonna see them again.

296
00:20:46,302 --> 00:20:48,269
And I'm okay with that.

297
00:20:48,401 --> 00:20:51,736
Because I know if I die
out there, I'm dying for them.

298
00:20:52,902 --> 00:20:55,369
We lose one more time,
the Earth is gone.

299
00:20:55,501 --> 00:20:58,601
[Liu Kang] And our only chance
is to face this together.

300
00:20:58,736 --> 00:21:03,434
You, Johnny Cage,
are a part of this now.

301
00:21:08,235 --> 00:21:11,636
[heroic music builds, stops]

302
00:21:12,202 --> 00:21:13,434
Fuck that.

303
00:21:13,568 --> 00:21:14,902
[Sonya] Johnny,
even if you walk away,

304
00:21:15,035 --> 00:21:16,669
the Elder Gods
can still summon you to fight.

305
00:21:16,802 --> 00:21:17,769
Not if they can't find me.

306
00:21:17,902 --> 00:21:19,534
So what are you gonna do, huh?

307
00:21:19,669 --> 00:21:21,002
You just going to go hide?

308
00:21:21,135 --> 00:21:23,202
No, first I'm gonna drink
every beer on the planet,

309
00:21:23,335 --> 00:21:24,702
then I'm going to hide.

310
00:21:24,836 --> 00:21:26,302
Because this shit's
got nothing to do with me.

311
00:21:26,434 --> 00:21:28,269
I'm not some great warrior.

312
00:21:28,401 --> 00:21:29,702
I'm not some champion.

313
00:21:29,836 --> 00:21:32,135
Okay? I'm an actor.

314
00:21:32,269 --> 00:21:33,501
[Sonya] Hmm.

315
00:21:34,369 --> 00:21:35,636
And before that,
you were the guy

316
00:21:35,769 --> 00:21:38,135
with five black belts
and a world title.

317
00:21:39,968 --> 00:21:43,736
Yeah, I saw
some of those old fights.

318
00:21:43,869 --> 00:21:46,935
Man, you could have been
one of the best.

319
00:21:47,068 --> 00:21:49,836
But I wasn't.
And that was a long time ago.

320
00:21:49,968 --> 00:21:53,602
That guy you want
is dead and buried.

321
00:21:53,736 --> 00:21:56,068
Or maybe he's still in there
trying to get out.

322
00:22:16,434 --> 00:22:17,636
Hey, listen...

323
00:22:19,669 --> 00:22:21,836
I'm like 90% sure
I had an aneurysm

324
00:22:21,968 --> 00:22:24,569
and this is some kind of
fucked up coma dream,

325
00:22:26,235 --> 00:22:28,569
but on the off chance
this shit is real,

326
00:22:30,002 --> 00:22:32,168
best of luck with the whole
saving the world thing.

327
00:22:37,434 --> 00:22:39,002
[thunderclap]

328
00:22:39,135 --> 00:22:41,168
[thunder rumbling]

329
00:22:44,736 --> 00:22:47,269
[voices whispering]

330
00:22:47,401 --> 00:22:50,636
[Quan Chi] You should know
that when you died,

331
00:22:50,769 --> 00:22:55,468
it was not your so-called
friends who brought you back.

332
00:22:56,434 --> 00:22:58,602
It was not Lord Raiden,

333
00:22:59,369 --> 00:23:01,736
the Great Pretender.

334
00:23:03,235 --> 00:23:05,501
It was Shao Kahn.

335
00:23:06,569 --> 00:23:09,068
Rise now,

336
00:23:09,202 --> 00:23:12,636
as a champion of Outworld.

337
00:23:12,769 --> 00:23:15,501
[ominous music builds]

338
00:23:19,501 --> 00:23:23,068
[Acolyte 1] Sire,
we retrieved the package.

339
00:23:25,168 --> 00:23:26,702
Quan Chi!

340
00:23:26,836 --> 00:23:29,434
I am told you sent your
followers to Earthrealm.

341
00:23:29,569 --> 00:23:30,869
What were they doing there?

342
00:23:31,002 --> 00:23:34,401
Simply retrieving
some lost property, my lady.

343
00:23:34,535 --> 00:23:36,636
By order of your father.

344
00:23:39,068 --> 00:23:40,434
What is that?

345
00:23:44,602 --> 00:23:46,569
I believe it's called...

346
00:23:47,401 --> 00:23:48,769
a "Kano."

347
00:23:53,535 --> 00:23:55,569
[man] One Sling Dog, please.

348
00:23:58,002 --> 00:23:59,002
[gasps]

349
00:24:01,135 --> 00:24:03,235
You're Johnny Cage.

350
00:24:03,369 --> 00:24:04,902
That's what the tab says.

351
00:24:05,035 --> 00:24:06,636
[man] Holy shit.

352
00:24:06,769 --> 00:24:10,869
I freaking loved <i>Citizen Cage</i>
when I was a kid.

353
00:24:12,569 --> 00:24:14,168
Thanks, man. I appreciate it.

354
00:24:15,968 --> 00:24:18,636
Dude, you know
what they should do?

355
00:24:18,769 --> 00:24:21,401
They should
do another <i>Citizen Cage.</i>

356
00:24:21,535 --> 00:24:23,269
Like a reboot.

357
00:24:23,401 --> 00:24:25,802
Come on, man.
Give me a break.

358
00:24:25,935 --> 00:24:28,035
-Nobody wants that.
-What?

359
00:24:28,168 --> 00:24:29,702
You think the world
is crying out

360
00:24:29,836 --> 00:24:33,569
for a Johnny Cage comeback?
Huh?

361
00:24:33,702 --> 00:24:36,035
No. They want gritty,
they want grounded,

362
00:24:36,168 --> 00:24:37,569
they want Keanu Reeves

363
00:24:37,702 --> 00:24:39,401
murdering a thousand
fucking dudes with a pencil.

364
00:24:39,535 --> 00:24:41,502
That's what people wanna see.

365
00:24:43,235 --> 00:24:47,401
Not some dinosaur
doing a bunch of karate poses.

366
00:24:48,401 --> 00:24:50,435
That shit went out
in the '90's.

367
00:24:54,269 --> 00:24:56,002
I thought it was pretty cool.

368
00:25:06,502 --> 00:25:08,035
[sighs]

369
00:25:16,702 --> 00:25:19,769
[Quan Chi
chanting indistinctly]

370
00:25:22,369 --> 00:25:24,636
[unsettling music playing]

371
00:25:31,202 --> 00:25:33,402
[continues chanting]

372
00:25:35,569 --> 00:25:37,102
[Kano screams]

373
00:25:41,235 --> 00:25:43,535
Where's my fucking eye?

374
00:25:43,669 --> 00:25:45,902
-[squelching]
-[Kano grunts]

375
00:25:47,102 --> 00:25:48,168
Blondie.

376
00:25:49,502 --> 00:25:51,335
[Raiden] The tournament
has begun.

377
00:25:51,469 --> 00:25:53,535
Today you fight
for Earthrealm.

378
00:25:53,669 --> 00:25:56,068
For the lives of everyone
you have ever known.

379
00:25:56,202 --> 00:25:59,636
If you fail,
the Earth fails with you.

380
00:25:59,769 --> 00:26:03,402
Two of our champions will
be chosen to compete today.

381
00:26:03,535 --> 00:26:04,669
The winners will advance

382
00:26:04,802 --> 00:26:06,669
to the next stage
of the tournament.

383
00:26:06,802 --> 00:26:09,836
The losers will be eliminated.

384
00:26:09,968 --> 00:26:10,702
To the death.

385
00:26:10,836 --> 00:26:12,769
That is up to the winner.

386
00:26:13,669 --> 00:26:15,235
Maybe don't lose.

387
00:26:15,370 --> 00:26:16,902
[energy whooshing]

388
00:26:18,535 --> 00:26:19,935
[pulsing]

389
00:26:20,902 --> 00:26:22,702
Well, looks like
it's my lucky day.

390
00:26:22,836 --> 00:26:25,168
Blade, you got this.

391
00:26:31,002 --> 00:26:33,002
I thought you said
two of us were fighting.

392
00:26:34,068 --> 00:26:37,535
[rock music
playing over stereo]

393
00:26:37,669 --> 00:26:41,469
[announcer] <i>It's Johnny Cage</i>
<i>with a brutal hit. He's down.</i>

394
00:26:41,602 --> 00:26:43,102
-[whistle blows]
-[announcer] <i>It's official.</i>

395
00:26:43,235 --> 00:26:45,869
<i>Johnny Cage just became</i>
<i>the youngest minor</i>

396
00:26:46,002 --> 00:26:47,602
<i>to ever win this tournament.</i>

397
00:26:47,736 --> 00:26:50,569
<i>This young man</i>
<i>is destined for greatness.</i>

398
00:26:53,935 --> 00:26:56,702
[bartender] You seem
a little down, Johnny.

399
00:26:56,836 --> 00:26:58,935
You're normally
a little more animated.

400
00:27:05,535 --> 00:27:07,135
<i>Uno mas,</i> thanks, Ed.

401
00:27:10,402 --> 00:27:11,602
[zaps]

402
00:27:17,235 --> 00:27:18,702
[grunts]

403
00:27:27,235 --> 00:27:29,402
Oh, shit.

404
00:27:29,535 --> 00:27:32,168
[suspenseful music playing]

405
00:27:34,202 --> 00:27:35,469
I don't know
what you're on about.

406
00:27:35,602 --> 00:27:37,035
The amulet of what now?

407
00:27:37,168 --> 00:27:38,802
Shinnok. Pay attention!

408
00:27:38,935 --> 00:27:40,602
Don't look at me
with that tone of voice,

409
00:27:40,736 --> 00:27:42,102
you big bleached dildo.

410
00:27:42,235 --> 00:27:44,370
I've just been dead.
And my fucking eye's AWOL.

411
00:27:44,502 --> 00:27:48,068
Stop your incessant whinging.
We can build you another.

412
00:27:48,202 --> 00:27:50,002
Why is he not a Revenant
like the rest of them?

413
00:27:50,135 --> 00:27:52,702
[Quan Chi] He was not worth
the time or the effort.

414
00:27:52,836 --> 00:27:55,469
This one barely has a soul
left to corrupt.

415
00:27:55,602 --> 00:27:57,702
Ha! You hear that?
A fucking loophole.

416
00:27:57,836 --> 00:27:59,270
[laughs] Go, you good thing.

417
00:27:59,402 --> 00:28:02,535
Where is the amulet you took
from Raiden's temple?

418
00:28:02,669 --> 00:28:04,002
I don't know,
probably in my pocket

419
00:28:04,135 --> 00:28:05,802
where I keep
all the shit I steal.

420
00:28:07,370 --> 00:28:09,102
Oh, right-oh.

421
00:28:11,236 --> 00:28:15,336
-Here we go. How about...
-[metal clinking]

422
00:28:15,469 --> 00:28:18,236
Nah, different temple.
Well, hold on.

423
00:28:18,370 --> 00:28:19,736
This could be...

424
00:28:19,869 --> 00:28:21,935
[chuckles] Yeah.
Should call her.

425
00:28:22,702 --> 00:28:25,902
Ah! Here we are. Yahtzee.

426
00:28:26,435 --> 00:28:27,370
Oi!

427
00:28:27,502 --> 00:28:28,535
We could have left him dead.

428
00:28:28,669 --> 00:28:30,435
Hey! First off, fuck off.

429
00:28:30,569 --> 00:28:32,569
And you,
where are you going with that?

430
00:28:33,569 --> 00:28:35,168
I will take it to my father.

431
00:28:36,535 --> 00:28:37,769
Unfortunately, Princess,

432
00:28:37,902 --> 00:28:40,402
it appears
you are needed elsewhere.

433
00:28:42,636 --> 00:28:44,303
Oi, you creepy fucking mime.

434
00:28:44,435 --> 00:28:46,569
I stole that fair and square.

435
00:28:47,569 --> 00:28:48,869
Good luck.

436
00:28:55,769 --> 00:28:58,402
[footsteps thudding]

437
00:29:01,502 --> 00:29:03,669
[thrilling music playing]

438
00:29:09,669 --> 00:29:12,336
[Kitana] Each flame
represents a fighter.

439
00:29:12,502 --> 00:29:13,669
The tournament ends
when one side

440
00:29:13,802 --> 00:29:15,602
has no champions left.

441
00:29:16,469 --> 00:29:18,002
Hey. How's it going, babe?

442
00:29:18,135 --> 00:29:20,035
[blades clanking]

443
00:29:20,169 --> 00:29:23,336
Listen, I'm warning you,

444
00:29:23,469 --> 00:29:26,502
I got a Saturn Award for
best fight in a feature film,

445
00:29:26,636 --> 00:29:28,203
so don't mess with me.

446
00:29:28,336 --> 00:29:30,102
[gong tolls]

447
00:29:32,203 --> 00:29:34,203
Whoa! Whoa. Easy, all right.

448
00:29:34,336 --> 00:29:36,736
Let's just take a timeout here
and talk about it.

449
00:29:36,869 --> 00:29:39,869
Okay? I really don't feel
comfortable hitting a girl.

450
00:29:41,469 --> 00:29:43,836
Don't worry, you won't.

451
00:29:49,535 --> 00:29:51,502
[blades slashing]

452
00:29:53,303 --> 00:29:54,935
[both grunting]

453
00:29:55,068 --> 00:29:57,102
Whoa! Come on. Easy.
Let's just talk about this.

454
00:30:01,736 --> 00:30:03,636
-[grunts]
-[thuds]

455
00:30:20,002 --> 00:30:21,435
Why are you so fucking mean?

456
00:30:21,569 --> 00:30:22,836
[Kitana scoffs]

457
00:30:25,035 --> 00:30:26,669
[panting]

458
00:30:32,035 --> 00:30:33,569
[Johnny grunting]

459
00:30:46,669 --> 00:30:48,569
[both grunting]

460
00:30:48,702 --> 00:30:49,935
[Kitana grunts]

461
00:31:12,435 --> 00:31:13,602
[grunts]

462
00:31:16,869 --> 00:31:18,103
[sighs]

463
00:31:18,236 --> 00:31:20,169
[thrilling music continues]

464
00:31:35,469 --> 00:31:37,669
[blades slashing]

465
00:31:41,435 --> 00:31:42,769
[grunts]

466
00:31:45,469 --> 00:31:47,736
-[blades slash]
-[groans]

467
00:31:55,736 --> 00:31:57,902
[Johnny grunts]

468
00:32:03,836 --> 00:32:04,769
[groans]

469
00:32:14,003 --> 00:32:15,435
Finish him!

470
00:32:29,535 --> 00:32:30,869
Hmm.

471
00:32:46,270 --> 00:32:49,569
[suspenseful music playing]

472
00:32:54,802 --> 00:32:57,502
[Sindel] It appears your side
is already down a man.

473
00:32:58,469 --> 00:32:59,736
Tragic.

474
00:33:02,636 --> 00:33:03,869
And who are you?

475
00:33:04,003 --> 00:33:06,669
Sindel. High Queen of Edenia.

476
00:33:06,802 --> 00:33:09,370
Consort to the great
Shao Kahn.

477
00:33:09,502 --> 00:33:11,402
They send their queen
to fight?

478
00:33:11,535 --> 00:33:14,902
No. We send our best to fight.

479
00:33:15,303 --> 00:33:16,736
Oh.

480
00:33:16,869 --> 00:33:18,902
No offense, babe, but you look
really fucking dead.

481
00:33:19,036 --> 00:33:21,370
I was freed
from my mortal bonds.

482
00:33:21,502 --> 00:33:22,636
Shao Kahn showed me

483
00:33:22,769 --> 00:33:24,336
the pleasures
of a life eternal.

484
00:33:24,469 --> 00:33:26,136
-[gong tolls]
-[metal clanks]

485
00:33:28,903 --> 00:33:30,969
Perhaps I'll do the same
for you.

486
00:33:31,103 --> 00:33:32,836
[metal clanking]

487
00:33:36,303 --> 00:33:37,602
[Sonya yells]

488
00:33:40,769 --> 00:33:43,069
What a pretty trick.

489
00:33:43,203 --> 00:33:45,435
Would you like to see mine?

490
00:33:45,569 --> 00:33:47,469
No, actually I'm good.

491
00:33:48,535 --> 00:33:50,869
-[grunts]
-[screaming]

492
00:33:55,236 --> 00:33:56,569
[yelling]

493
00:34:00,903 --> 00:34:01,903
[grunts]

494
00:34:02,036 --> 00:34:03,036
[metal slashing]

495
00:34:08,270 --> 00:34:10,270
[screaming]

496
00:34:10,402 --> 00:34:13,103
[Sonya] Fuck you!
You stupid bitch!

497
00:34:16,069 --> 00:34:17,136
[grunts]

498
00:34:23,502 --> 00:34:24,602
[grunts]

499
00:34:26,236 --> 00:34:27,535
[groans]

500
00:34:30,136 --> 00:34:32,535
[both straining]

501
00:34:32,669 --> 00:34:34,136
[Sindel growling]

502
00:34:38,502 --> 00:34:40,402
[screaming]

503
00:34:41,069 --> 00:34:42,169
[thuds]

504
00:34:48,502 --> 00:34:50,069
[Sonya grunting]

505
00:34:56,602 --> 00:34:59,535
[both straining]

506
00:34:59,669 --> 00:35:01,702
[screaming]

507
00:35:07,402 --> 00:35:08,702
[Sonya grunts]

508
00:35:13,303 --> 00:35:14,636
[squelches]

509
00:35:16,535 --> 00:35:17,936
[panting]

510
00:35:19,669 --> 00:35:21,803
It appears
our sides are now even.

511
00:35:26,870 --> 00:35:28,736
What'd I miss? [sighs]

512
00:35:28,870 --> 00:35:31,402
Fuck yeah! Look who's back.

513
00:35:32,870 --> 00:35:35,069
Well? How bad was it?

514
00:35:35,203 --> 00:35:38,569
Zombie queen.
Pit of spikes. Yeah.

515
00:35:38,702 --> 00:35:40,370
-So pretty goddamn bad.
-Ow.

516
00:35:40,502 --> 00:35:42,003
-[groans]
-[Sonya grunts]

517
00:35:42,136 --> 00:35:43,602
-You okay?
-Yeah.

518
00:35:48,069 --> 00:35:49,136
What happened?

519
00:35:49,270 --> 00:35:51,602
You were eliminated
from the tournament.

520
00:35:52,469 --> 00:35:53,936
You lost.

521
00:35:54,069 --> 00:35:56,770
You are lucky, she was
charitable and let you live.

522
00:36:04,402 --> 00:36:05,936
[Kano] Oi! Pennywise.

523
00:36:06,069 --> 00:36:08,336
I've been looking all over
this shithole for you.

524
00:36:08,469 --> 00:36:09,870
You promised me a new eye.

525
00:36:10,003 --> 00:36:12,003
And it better be one
that shoots lasers.

526
00:36:12,136 --> 00:36:15,036
-I have other priorities.
-[Kano] Like fucking what?

527
00:36:15,169 --> 00:36:16,702
If it's putting on
more eyeliner,

528
00:36:16,837 --> 00:36:18,336
trust me, you're good.

529
00:36:18,469 --> 00:36:19,770
All right? Come on, mate.

530
00:36:19,903 --> 00:36:22,069
I am bumping into shit
left, right, and center.

531
00:36:22,203 --> 00:36:24,103
I mean, my peripheral vision
is fucked.

532
00:36:24,236 --> 00:36:25,737
Proper fucked, mate.

533
00:36:25,870 --> 00:36:27,936
So come on.
Chop-chop. Let's get to it.

534
00:36:28,069 --> 00:36:29,435
[pulsing]

535
00:36:29,569 --> 00:36:31,003
Well, you don't have
to do it right now.

536
00:36:31,136 --> 00:36:33,837
I mean, you need to,
you know, take a measurement.

537
00:36:33,969 --> 00:36:37,569
Check the color or wash
your grubby little hands.

538
00:36:40,402 --> 00:36:41,837
All right, let's have a look.

539
00:36:41,969 --> 00:36:44,903
Don't fucking roll it on
the fucking ground, you grub!

540
00:36:46,270 --> 00:36:48,435
Oi, the amulet.

541
00:36:48,569 --> 00:36:50,969
I want that back.
And don't fucking roll it.

542
00:36:51,103 --> 00:36:53,837
[Quan Chi] You got your eye.
Now leave me alone.

543
00:36:53,969 --> 00:36:56,535
The amulet
does not belong to you.

544
00:36:56,669 --> 00:36:58,469
Its powers are well beyond

545
00:36:58,602 --> 00:37:00,703
-your meager understanding.
-[blows air]

546
00:37:00,837 --> 00:37:02,069
Idiot.

547
00:37:02,203 --> 00:37:03,936
All right. Let's take
this baby for a test drive.

548
00:37:04,837 --> 00:37:07,636
All right.
[inhales deeply]

549
00:37:07,770 --> 00:37:12,770
One, two, three.
Oh! Fuck! Snug.

550
00:37:12,903 --> 00:37:15,502
[zapping]

551
00:37:15,636 --> 00:37:17,136
Wow. [chuckles]

552
00:37:17,270 --> 00:37:19,670
Holy shit, is that HD?
That's pretty good.

553
00:37:19,803 --> 00:37:22,535
How many eyes you made?
Can you do me other one?

554
00:37:35,602 --> 00:37:37,703
You seem troubled, Mr. Cage.

555
00:37:39,336 --> 00:37:41,435
Yeah. Well, 'cause of me

556
00:37:41,569 --> 00:37:44,203
Earth's odds
just got 20% worse.

557
00:37:44,336 --> 00:37:46,637
I had a chance to actually
do something worth a damn

558
00:37:46,770 --> 00:37:48,203
and I screwed it all up.

559
00:37:48,336 --> 00:37:52,803
So, yeah, I'd say "troubled"
just about sums it up.

560
00:37:53,936 --> 00:37:55,670
[rustling]

561
00:38:00,703 --> 00:38:03,936
What are those? Pills?

562
00:38:04,402 --> 00:38:06,103
Huh?

563
00:38:06,236 --> 00:38:07,770
Are they magic fighting pills?

564
00:38:08,837 --> 00:38:10,969
Is that how
you get your powers?

565
00:38:17,969 --> 00:38:19,569
[clattering]

566
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:21,502
Bird seed.

567
00:38:22,837 --> 00:38:27,136
Oh. Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Bird seed. Yeah.

568
00:38:27,270 --> 00:38:30,703
Well, I thought you were gonna
give me some kind of lecture,

569
00:38:30,837 --> 00:38:34,737
but, yeah, chores are good.

570
00:38:37,203 --> 00:38:39,069
You don't need a lecture.

571
00:38:39,203 --> 00:38:40,502
You need perspective.

572
00:38:40,637 --> 00:38:43,003
[scoffs] Perspective, huh?

573
00:38:43,136 --> 00:38:45,435
There are eight billion people
on this planet

574
00:38:45,569 --> 00:38:47,603
and yet the gods chose you.

575
00:38:47,737 --> 00:38:49,670
Perhaps they saw
your true potential

576
00:38:49,803 --> 00:38:52,270
-as a champion of Earthrealm.
-[sighs]

577
00:38:52,402 --> 00:38:53,969
Maybe they made a mistake.

578
00:38:54,103 --> 00:38:55,270
Maybe.

579
00:38:55,402 --> 00:38:58,670
If I see the Elder Gods,
I'll be sure to tell them.

580
00:39:03,136 --> 00:39:06,703
Well, I'm glad
you find this all so amusing.

581
00:39:06,837 --> 00:39:10,637
Hey, great pep talk,
by the way. Just nailed it.

582
00:39:15,136 --> 00:39:17,570
[pensive music playing]

583
00:39:23,136 --> 00:39:24,969
[rumbling]

584
00:39:40,036 --> 00:39:42,003
[crackling]

585
00:39:44,637 --> 00:39:46,570
[thunder crashing]

586
00:39:56,303 --> 00:39:57,502
Ouch.

587
00:39:58,536 --> 00:40:00,536
You have done this before?

588
00:40:01,336 --> 00:40:02,737
I've seen it done.

589
00:40:04,536 --> 00:40:05,703
[Sonya] All right.

590
00:40:10,870 --> 00:40:14,570
It's okay. The Princess Kitana
has been my eyes and ears

591
00:40:14,703 --> 00:40:16,803
inside the palace
for many years now.

592
00:40:18,136 --> 00:40:20,303
We know the risk you took
coming here.

593
00:40:20,469 --> 00:40:21,703
Thank you, Kitana.

594
00:40:21,837 --> 00:40:24,036
Wait, are you telling me
I got my ass kicked

595
00:40:24,169 --> 00:40:25,435
by one of the good guys?

596
00:40:25,570 --> 00:40:28,936
I had to make it look real.
He was watching.

597
00:40:29,069 --> 00:40:31,270
They found
the Amulet of Shinnok.

598
00:40:31,402 --> 00:40:32,536
It was in the possession

599
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:34,370
of a dead sellsword
named Kano.

600
00:40:34,503 --> 00:40:35,936
Son of a bitch.

601
00:40:36,069 --> 00:40:37,936
If the Emperor finds a way
to charge the amulet,

602
00:40:38,069 --> 00:40:39,637
he would be unstoppable.

603
00:40:39,770 --> 00:40:41,303
It would be
like fighting a god.

604
00:40:41,435 --> 00:40:44,503
Yeah, well, let's not do that.

605
00:40:44,637 --> 00:40:47,435
My friend
is in the tournament.

606
00:40:47,570 --> 00:40:50,003
Jade was raised
under Shao Kahn's army.

607
00:40:50,136 --> 00:40:54,402
Do what you must,
but do not make her suffer.

608
00:40:55,402 --> 00:40:56,936
[crackling]

609
00:41:06,402 --> 00:41:08,536
You went to another realm?

610
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:11,870
You followed me?

611
00:41:12,003 --> 00:41:14,203
I am trying to keep you alive.

612
00:41:14,336 --> 00:41:15,637
By spying on your friend.

613
00:41:15,770 --> 00:41:18,069
By keeping my friend
from making a mistake.

614
00:41:18,203 --> 00:41:21,670
You are conspiring
with Lord Raiden. The enemy.

615
00:41:21,803 --> 00:41:24,770
I swore an oath, Kitana.

616
00:41:24,903 --> 00:41:28,703
To serve as Shao Kahn's sword.

617
00:41:35,936 --> 00:41:37,670
[Raiden] The second round
of the tournament

618
00:41:37,803 --> 00:41:40,270
will consist of three matches.

619
00:41:40,402 --> 00:41:43,470
Jax, Cole, Liu Kang.

620
00:41:50,436 --> 00:41:51,969
[metal slashes]

621
00:41:56,936 --> 00:41:58,069
[gasps]

622
00:42:00,637 --> 00:42:02,136
Kung Lao.

623
00:42:03,270 --> 00:42:04,936
I have been given new life.

624
00:42:06,236 --> 00:42:07,703
My son?

625
00:42:07,837 --> 00:42:09,403
[chiming]

626
00:42:09,536 --> 00:42:11,536
[energy pulsing]

627
00:42:16,637 --> 00:42:20,270
Look at that.
Still part of this tournament.

628
00:42:20,403 --> 00:42:21,903
But that's not why I'm here.

629
00:42:23,436 --> 00:42:25,837
[ominous choral music playing]

630
00:42:30,969 --> 00:42:32,837
No!

631
00:42:32,969 --> 00:42:34,069
No!

632
00:42:41,603 --> 00:42:43,903
[groaning]

633
00:42:45,503 --> 00:42:46,969
Attack now!

634
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:52,270
[Sonya grunting]

635
00:42:52,403 --> 00:42:54,536
[tense music playing]

636
00:42:56,969 --> 00:42:58,103
[grunts]

637
00:43:02,236 --> 00:43:03,870
[choking]

638
00:43:14,969 --> 00:43:17,036
[grunting]

639
00:43:21,969 --> 00:43:23,436
[zaps]

640
00:43:25,470 --> 00:43:31,136
Imagine what one
could do with such power.

641
00:43:31,270 --> 00:43:36,069
[Shao Kahn] Careful, Sorcerer,
that doesn't belong to you.

642
00:43:43,470 --> 00:43:46,436
The amulet must be bound
to a mortal soul.

643
00:43:46,570 --> 00:43:48,403
Once it has imprinted
on to you,

644
00:43:48,536 --> 00:43:50,837
Raiden's power will be yours.

645
00:43:50,969 --> 00:43:53,436
The amulet
will give you immortality.

646
00:43:53,570 --> 00:43:55,304
[amulet pulsing]

647
00:43:55,436 --> 00:43:57,737
[dramatic music playing]

648
00:43:58,470 --> 00:44:00,036
[Shao Kahn grunting]

649
00:44:05,637 --> 00:44:07,503
[Shao Kahn growls]

650
00:44:15,103 --> 00:44:18,069
[inhales, growls]

651
00:44:18,203 --> 00:44:20,337
[bubbling]

652
00:44:20,470 --> 00:44:23,870
[gate rattling]

653
00:44:24,803 --> 00:44:27,969
[suspenseful music playing]

654
00:44:33,304 --> 00:44:34,837
[growls]

655
00:44:52,670 --> 00:44:54,503
[portal whooshing]

656
00:44:57,271 --> 00:45:00,936
Well, this is fucking ominous.

657
00:45:03,069 --> 00:45:04,703
[portal whooshing]

658
00:45:07,603 --> 00:45:09,371
I'm guessing you're Jade.

659
00:45:09,503 --> 00:45:11,403
Let's get this over with.

660
00:45:12,136 --> 00:45:13,136
[clangs]

661
00:45:15,271 --> 00:45:16,837
[suit pulsing]

662
00:45:16,969 --> 00:45:19,703
I am told you carry
the blood of Scorpion.

663
00:45:23,737 --> 00:45:25,870
I look forward to spilling it.

664
00:45:29,003 --> 00:45:30,136
[Jax yells]

665
00:45:40,136 --> 00:45:42,470
You know you're fighting
on the wrong side, right?

666
00:45:43,204 --> 00:45:44,403
[grunts]

667
00:45:50,903 --> 00:45:52,837
[staff clangs, pulsing]

668
00:45:52,969 --> 00:45:55,136
What the fuck
do you have under there?

669
00:45:56,403 --> 00:45:58,637
Shit. [yells]

670
00:46:10,103 --> 00:46:11,603
[panting]

671
00:46:12,436 --> 00:46:13,969
[yells]

672
00:46:18,470 --> 00:46:19,637
Well, hello there.

673
00:46:21,969 --> 00:46:23,137
[yelling]

674
00:46:27,870 --> 00:46:30,670
[Shao Kahn] I hope
your ancestors are watching.

675
00:46:32,670 --> 00:46:34,637
[thrilling music playing]

676
00:46:43,204 --> 00:46:44,137
[Cole yells]

677
00:46:44,271 --> 00:46:45,637
[metal clangs]

678
00:46:47,003 --> 00:46:49,069
-[yells]
-[Shao Kahn grunts]

679
00:46:51,870 --> 00:46:52,969
[growls]

680
00:46:55,436 --> 00:46:56,637
[yells]

681
00:46:59,403 --> 00:47:00,603
[Jade yells]

682
00:47:02,104 --> 00:47:05,536
For what it is worth,
I take no joy in this.

683
00:47:08,104 --> 00:47:10,403
Then you're really going
to hate this shit.

684
00:47:11,237 --> 00:47:13,670
-[yells]
-[groans]

685
00:47:14,070 --> 00:47:15,503
[coughs]

686
00:47:15,637 --> 00:47:17,170
This is for my family.

687
00:47:18,371 --> 00:47:20,371
For my friends.

688
00:47:20,503 --> 00:47:23,036
For every moment
that brought me here.

689
00:47:23,170 --> 00:47:26,870
This is for Earth,
you son of a bitch.

690
00:47:28,371 --> 00:47:30,003
[dramatic choral music playing]

691
00:47:32,637 --> 00:47:34,104
[Cole grunts]

692
00:47:39,670 --> 00:47:41,170
[Shao Kahn grunts]

693
00:47:41,304 --> 00:47:42,803
[armor clanging]

694
00:47:44,603 --> 00:47:46,903
-[blade slicing]
-[blood splattering]

695
00:47:59,337 --> 00:48:00,770
[strains]

696
00:48:02,037 --> 00:48:03,204
[groans]

697
00:48:03,337 --> 00:48:05,536
[suit pulsing, powering up]

698
00:48:08,170 --> 00:48:10,204
[Shao Kahn screams]

699
00:48:10,337 --> 00:48:11,403
[Shao Kahn groans in pain]

700
00:48:11,536 --> 00:48:13,737
[squelching]

701
00:48:15,271 --> 00:48:16,436
[Cole] What?

702
00:48:17,070 --> 00:48:19,436
[laughs]

703
00:48:20,371 --> 00:48:21,470
[gasps]

704
00:48:21,603 --> 00:48:23,004
[Shao Kahn yells]

705
00:48:25,204 --> 00:48:27,803
-[gasps]
-[squelching]

706
00:48:31,137 --> 00:48:32,803
[exhales]

707
00:48:38,503 --> 00:48:40,770
[liquid sizzles]

708
00:48:40,903 --> 00:48:43,137
Give my regards to the dead.

709
00:48:44,237 --> 00:48:45,237
[weapon splashing]

710
00:48:45,371 --> 00:48:47,037
[groans]

711
00:48:47,170 --> 00:48:48,903
[grunts, pants]

712
00:48:51,969 --> 00:48:54,837
Go on, do it.

713
00:49:18,271 --> 00:49:19,803
Why?

714
00:49:19,936 --> 00:49:22,070
Your friend spared
one of our guys.

715
00:49:23,271 --> 00:49:24,403
Now we're even.

716
00:49:25,271 --> 00:49:27,970
By the way, hell of a fight.

717
00:49:30,436 --> 00:49:32,937
[energy warbling]

718
00:49:36,637 --> 00:49:38,536
[portal whooshing]

719
00:49:42,703 --> 00:49:45,170
[blade whirring, vibrating]

720
00:49:50,536 --> 00:49:54,237
Kung Lao,
what have they done to you?

721
00:49:54,371 --> 00:49:56,470
Opened my eyes to the truth.

722
00:49:59,037 --> 00:50:00,237
What truth?

723
00:50:00,371 --> 00:50:05,603
Look around. The gods have
abandoned their creation.

724
00:50:05,737 --> 00:50:08,570
Only Shao Kahn
can save us now.

725
00:50:08,703 --> 00:50:12,070
One of those gods raised you.
Loved you.

726
00:50:13,603 --> 00:50:15,170
And you slit his throat.

727
00:50:18,104 --> 00:50:19,403
[grunts]

728
00:50:20,470 --> 00:50:21,337
[thuds]

729
00:50:21,470 --> 00:50:23,037
[tense music playing]

730
00:51:12,937 --> 00:51:14,104
[scraping]

731
00:51:18,838 --> 00:51:20,637
-[growls]
-[Liu Kang grunts]

732
00:51:20,770 --> 00:51:24,937
Stop. Kung Lao,
remember who you are!

733
00:51:26,304 --> 00:51:27,871
You were my brother.

734
00:51:28,004 --> 00:51:31,470
And when you're dead,
when your realm falls,

735
00:51:31,603 --> 00:51:33,170
we will be brothers again.

736
00:51:33,304 --> 00:51:34,503
[straining]

737
00:51:35,271 --> 00:51:36,670
[grunts]

738
00:51:42,703 --> 00:51:44,970
[sinister choral music playing]

739
00:51:58,637 --> 00:52:00,603
Don't make me do this.

740
00:52:03,304 --> 00:52:04,871
[thrilling music playing]

741
00:52:34,536 --> 00:52:35,804
[straining]

742
00:52:36,904 --> 00:52:37,737
[grunts]

743
00:52:37,871 --> 00:52:39,937
[dramatic choral music playing]

744
00:53:02,503 --> 00:53:03,771
[clangs]

745
00:53:04,637 --> 00:53:05,838
[thuds]

746
00:53:11,037 --> 00:53:12,037
[whirring]

747
00:53:21,470 --> 00:53:23,503
I'll find a way to save you.

748
00:53:24,104 --> 00:53:25,503
[grunts]

749
00:53:28,104 --> 00:53:29,470
[grinding]

750
00:53:36,403 --> 00:53:38,436
I'm going to bring you back.

751
00:53:48,570 --> 00:53:49,771
[blow thuds]

752
00:53:52,304 --> 00:53:53,470
[squelching]

753
00:53:53,603 --> 00:53:55,570
[gurgling]

754
00:54:01,037 --> 00:54:02,170
[grinding stops]

755
00:54:07,037 --> 00:54:08,570
[groans, shudders]

756
00:54:13,738 --> 00:54:17,037
But not today, brother.

757
00:54:25,738 --> 00:54:27,804
[somber music playing]

758
00:54:36,638 --> 00:54:38,771
-[crackling]
-Raiden!

759
00:54:43,070 --> 00:54:46,470
-Is he?
-He's alive. Barely.

760
00:54:52,204 --> 00:54:53,771
He's been asking for you.

761
00:54:55,271 --> 00:54:56,704
[weakly] Liu Kang.

762
00:55:03,904 --> 00:55:05,271
My son.

763
00:55:05,403 --> 00:55:06,638
[exhales]

764
00:55:15,371 --> 00:55:16,671
What happened?

765
00:55:19,137 --> 00:55:20,137
I killed him.

766
00:55:21,337 --> 00:55:22,838
I didn't have a choice.

767
00:55:23,503 --> 00:55:24,604
I'm sorry.

768
00:55:29,004 --> 00:55:30,037
Where's Cole?

769
00:55:32,337 --> 00:55:33,904
He didn't come back?

770
00:55:36,937 --> 00:55:38,904
Oh, shit.

771
00:55:40,904 --> 00:55:41,904
[sighs]

772
00:55:50,304 --> 00:55:52,004
[Shao Kahn] Necromancer,

773
00:55:52,838 --> 00:55:55,403
give me your greatest warrior.

774
00:55:56,304 --> 00:55:58,771
The one they call Sub-Zero.

775
00:56:00,738 --> 00:56:02,738
[echoing] <i>Bi-Han.</i>

776
00:56:12,671 --> 00:56:14,738
[Quan Chi] <i>Rise now.</i>

777
00:56:17,738 --> 00:56:20,671
[sinister music playing]

778
