[Kitana screams]

1301
01:36:54,140 --> 01:36:56,006
[both grunting]

1302
01:37:09,240 --> 01:37:10,773
[screams]

1303
01:37:23,673 --> 01:37:25,140
[both grunting]

1304
01:37:26,606 --> 01:37:28,706
[choking]

1305
01:37:37,107 --> 01:37:39,006
[choking]

1306
01:37:48,873 --> 01:37:51,972
Weak. Just like your father.

1307
01:37:53,374 --> 01:37:55,506
[sentimental music playing]

1308
01:38:06,506 --> 01:38:08,406
[Jerrod] <i>Be strong, Kitana.</i>

1309
01:38:09,107 --> 01:38:10,539
[gasps]

1310
01:38:13,040 --> 01:38:14,140
[Kitana grunts]

1311
01:38:14,274 --> 01:38:16,606
[dramatic choral music playing]

1312
01:38:29,906 --> 01:38:33,107
It's time for them to see you
for what you really are.

1313
01:38:34,539 --> 01:38:36,040
[Kitana yells]

1314
01:38:41,374 --> 01:38:42,706
Mortal.

1315
01:38:44,374 --> 01:38:45,906
[screaming]

1316
01:38:46,606 --> 01:38:48,473
[whirring]

1317
01:38:57,773 --> 01:39:00,806
[indistinct chatter]

1318
01:39:05,207 --> 01:39:07,040
Stop. No.

1319
01:39:08,506 --> 01:39:12,040
Please stand. Stand. Please.

1320
01:39:19,140 --> 01:39:21,573
We are proud Edenians.

1321
01:39:22,439 --> 01:39:24,539
We do not kneel.

1322
01:39:30,740 --> 01:39:33,873
[woman chanting]
Kitana, our queen!

1323
01:39:35,374 --> 01:39:39,506
Kitana, our queen!

1324
01:39:39,640 --> 01:39:43,439
[citizens chanting]
Kitana, our queen!

1325
01:39:43,573 --> 01:39:45,873
[continues chanting]

1326
01:39:54,240 --> 01:39:56,107
[triumphant music playing]

1327
01:40:11,340 --> 01:40:13,706
[Johnny] <i>You want to know</i>
<i>what makes a hero?</i>

1328
01:40:15,173 --> 01:40:16,940
[sweeping music playing]

1329
01:40:18,307 --> 01:40:20,073
<i>It's not destiny.</i>

1330
01:40:20,207 --> 01:40:22,606
<i>It's not something</i>
<i>you're born with.</i>

1331
01:40:24,307 --> 01:40:26,439
<i>It's discovering that</i>
<i>sometimes</i>

1332
01:40:26,573 --> 01:40:27,907
<i>even one small light</i>

1333
01:40:28,040 --> 01:40:31,806
<i>is enough to hold back</i>
<i>the darkness.</i>

1334
01:40:31,940 --> 01:40:34,740
<i>It's facing</i>
<i>unimaginable loss...</i>

1335
01:40:36,173 --> 01:40:39,140
<i>and finding peace</i>
<i>on the other side.</i>

1336
01:40:48,274 --> 01:40:50,973
<i>It's lifting up</i>
<i>the ones you love knowing...</i>

1337
01:40:54,173 --> 01:40:57,640
<i>that they'll be there</i>
<i>to catch you when you fall.</i>

1338
01:41:03,673 --> 01:41:05,940
<i>It's searching</i>
<i>for greatness,</i>

1339
01:41:07,940 --> 01:41:11,874
<i>then realizing you've had it</i>
<i>in you this entire time.</i>

1340
01:41:13,806 --> 01:41:15,706
I say all of this to Raiden

1341
01:41:15,841 --> 01:41:19,874
and he looks at me
and he says...

1342
01:41:20,007 --> 01:41:25,740
[imitating Raiden] "You have
taught us so much, Mr. Cage.

1343
01:41:25,874 --> 01:41:30,107
Thank you. Thank you
for sharing your wisdom."

1344
01:41:31,274 --> 01:41:33,173
And you know what I tell him?

1345
01:41:33,307 --> 01:41:35,007
What did you say?

1346
01:41:35,140 --> 01:41:37,473
I said,
"That ain't no wisdom, bub.

1347
01:41:37,606 --> 01:41:40,907
That's perspective."

1348
01:41:41,040 --> 01:41:42,173
[children laugh]

1349
01:41:42,307 --> 01:41:45,673
[Raiden] Strange.
That is not how I remember it.

1350
01:41:46,506 --> 01:41:48,506
Oh. Yo.

1351
01:41:48,640 --> 01:41:50,406
I was just telling these guys

1352
01:41:50,539 --> 01:41:53,173
how we saved
all the realms, together.

1353
01:41:53,307 --> 01:41:54,473
Oh.

1354
01:41:54,606 --> 01:41:56,307
[Johnny] All right. Look...

1355
01:41:56,439 --> 01:42:00,907
I may have taken one or two
creative liberties.

1356
01:42:01,040 --> 01:42:02,307
Behold!

1357
01:42:02,439 --> 01:42:05,940
The human female you rescued
from the pit of spikes.

1358
01:42:06,673 --> 01:42:07,973
Seriously?

1359
01:42:08,107 --> 01:42:10,307
Two or three
creative liberties.

1360
01:42:10,439 --> 01:42:12,207
You know,
I've got to give it to you,

1361
01:42:12,340 --> 01:42:14,473
I thought you'd go
running back to Hollywood
first chance you got.

1362
01:42:14,606 --> 01:42:16,606
I made a promise
to these guys.

1363
01:42:16,740 --> 01:42:18,140
Hollywood can wait.

1364
01:42:18,274 --> 01:42:19,740
[portal whooshing]

1365
01:42:20,539 --> 01:42:22,140
[Johnny] Oh, shit.

1366
01:42:22,274 --> 01:42:23,774
Tell me there's not
another tournament.

1367
01:42:23,907 --> 01:42:26,107
No. Outworld
has been defeated.

1368
01:42:26,240 --> 01:42:28,439
Earthrealm has been saved.

1369
01:42:28,573 --> 01:42:31,439
So, uh, what the fuck
are you doing here?

1370
01:42:31,573 --> 01:42:34,406
We have lost far too many
of our champions.

1371
01:42:34,539 --> 01:42:36,173
It's time to bring them home.

1372
01:42:36,307 --> 01:42:37,841
[lightning crackles]

1373
01:42:38,706 --> 01:42:40,841
Someone order a Necromancer?

1374
01:42:40,973 --> 01:42:42,740
He might look like
Voldemort's nut sack,

1375
01:42:42,874 --> 01:42:45,573
but trust me, we're gonna
need this fucker.

1376
01:42:46,706 --> 01:42:49,973
Hey, g'day, Blondie.
Long time no see.

1377
01:42:51,073 --> 01:42:52,807
You ready
for your next lesson?

1378
01:42:52,940 --> 01:42:56,007
For the glory
of Johnny Fucking Cage.

1379
01:42:56,741 --> 01:42:58,706
[Baraka grunts]

1380
01:42:58,841 --> 01:43:01,807
Let's go get our friends.
Then we kill Kano.

1381
01:43:03,573 --> 01:43:05,140
Yeah. Good.

1382
01:43:05,274 --> 01:43:07,107
[heroic music playing]

1383
